{"tid":2355833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"公司嚟咗個新同事竟然係做唔到嘢嘅老seafood","createTime":"2021-01-06T11:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T12:01:25.000Z","uid":311855,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"877fab894d543b63f9804d958d8180a5316d99ca","tid":2355833,"uid":311855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"上個月有個新同事嚟我公司 <br />\n40歲左右，成個伯父咁嘅樣<br />\n呢個人行為好有問題...<br />\n同客zoom meeting時訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講嘢1999，辭不達意，無組織，無邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做嘢慢，出一封信出咗大半日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做啲on9嘢，例如戴住勞工手套做office work<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有問題唔問同一team嘅我 走去問其他team<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日&quot;高手&quot; 前&quot;高手&quot; 後讚人地<br />\n我講佢反而唔聽<br />\n<br />\n差唔多同期嚟咗另一位後生新同事<br />\n條友已經係咁點個位新同事做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔止一個同事私底下咁話佢... <br />\n開會仲要坐老細同其他PM, GM隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當正自己大佬<br />\n<br />\n題外話：<br />\n今日佢出咗封信俾外人<br />\n我極力阻止佢 叫佢幾次都唔聽<br />\n封信title叫&quot;Thank you... &quot; <br />\n大細楷又整錯<br />\n我同佢講 覆返對方well noted咪算囉<br />\n佢又唔聽<br />\n好彩最後無出街<br />\n如果唔係實俾人笑到面都黃....<br />\n<br />\n點解呢啲人人工仲要高我咁多<br />\n咩世道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018ca43492a8f2198fe52b94bc676ea811c0bcf8","tid":2355833,"uid":65201,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:08:37.000Z","msg":"你由得佢亂搞，等佢衰左你咪上位"},{"pid":"84da7be4190bf7188a4beb9357d09ecdfc2380dc","tid":2355833,"uid":44854,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:09:13.000Z","msg":"On9做乜要教佢<br />\n唔怪得知你人工低過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420ab6336fb5a8626849fe98ed5c21ccbbbf1363","tid":2355833,"uid"